com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation

Class JsonTypeInfo.Value

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonTypeInfo.Value
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JacksonAnnotationValue<JsonTypeInfo>, Serializable
    Enclosing class:
    JsonTypeInfo

    public static class JsonTypeInfo.Value
extends Object
implements JacksonAnnotationValue<JsonTypeInfo>, Serializable
    Property that defines whether type serializer is allowed to omit writing of type id, in case that value written has type same as JsonTypeInfo.defaultImpl(). If true, omission is allowed (although writer may or may not be able to do that); if false, type id should always be written still. public boolean skipWritingDefault() default false;
    See Also:
